HEADWORD: nuclear resonance
<hw>nuclear resonance</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Physics)</fld> <def>The
resonance absorption of a gamma ray by a nucleus identical to the
nucleus that emitted the gamma ray.</def>⟦br⟧
